&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Previously, Dovecot allowed multiple failed login attempts within a single session without being properly detected by Netfilter. This has now been fixed.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>🌙🐄 LDAP/OIDC Status Update - We didn’t forget. We were just... testing!</title><link>https://mailcow.email/posts/2025/nightly-progress/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 15:50:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://mailcow.email/posts/2025/nightly-progress/</guid><category domain="https://mailcow.email/categories/news/">News</category><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>Moohoo everyone&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In this blog post, I&amp;rsquo;ll walk you through the current state of the nightly branch of mailcow. The biggest highlight is of course the support for external authentication sources.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To make this new feature as seamless and user-friendly as possible, we had to introduce some adjustments — you&amp;rsquo;ll see what I mean.&lt;/p>
